---
title: Spiced Roasted Squash and Beets with Nutty Quinoa and Feta
description: What can we say? This salad is packed, packed, packed with great ingredients. Tender butternut squash and beets tossed with filling grains and fresh greens all finished off with feta and seeds will have you licking the plate!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-roasted-squash-and-beets-493c67b2.jpg
